1.title: New Generation
1.plot: In the final round of the Beywheelz World Championships, Sho Tenma and his Soaring Wing Pegasus battle Jin Ryu and his Doom Fire Drago in a best out of three competition. As the head of the Executive Committee, Chairman Ryan, and his team watch, the battle begins. Jin wins the opening round which is a Crash battle, which means that Sho must win the next test or he loses the championship. The second installment is a Race battle and Sho manages to come out on top and tie the match. The final round is a Stunt Battle, which can only be won by a Sleep Out, and Sho rallies ...

4.title: The Wheeler of the Wilderness
4.plot: Leon travels to a desert town called San Miguel to find a Wheeler known as "The Strong Armed Outlaw." He arrives in town to find that the local gym has just been destroyed by a mysterious Wheeler. One of the gym members, Covey, tells Leon he is now going to find the person who destroyed the gym and make him pay. They catch up with the Wheeler, Jake, a member of the Dominators, and Covey loses to him in a battle. Leon and Jake decide to battle at dusk. 7.title: The Law of the Dominators
7.plot: Team Estrella have won the first match against the Dominators in the Judgment Bey tournament and both teams are preparing for the next match. Gigante sees that Sting has been punished by the Dominators' Team leaders for losing the first match and he vows not to let his brother David down in their battle against Nicole and Marche. The match starts and the teamwork of Nicole and Marche give them an early lead. Things look good for them until David surprises everyone by sacrificing his own brother's bey to win the match at the last second. The tournament is now tied one ...

8.title: Avenger on the Ice
8.plot: Leon is training hard as he will be battling Jake of the Dominators in the next match in the Judgment Bey tournament. Leon has a reputation for trying to overpower his opponents using brute strength and Team Estrella hopes he can battle calmly this time and not lose his cool. The battle begins and since it is taking place in an Ice Stadium, Jake's bey has the advantage as it does not slip as much as Leon's. Leon figures out how to compensate for this however and it looks like he has kept calm this time and he will win. At the last moment the stadium breaks apart and ...

11.title: The Shocking Truth
11.plot: Ryan shocks the members of Team Estrella by offering them a chance to become the new Dominators and work for him. He explains that he has done research into the history of beys and that he found a portal to new world where beys that no one in this world has ever seen exist. Sho and his friends are interested until they learn that Ryan only wishes to use their Beyweelz to battle these new beys, defeat them, and take them for himself. 12.title: The Wheeler Bond
12.plot: Sho and the rest of Team Estrella have arrived at DREAM Headquarters and announce that they are there to stop Ryan from achieving his plan to invade another world. They are at once set upon by numerous members of the Dominators and various battles ensue. While Covey battles a huge number of guards by himself, Marche and Nicole take on David and Jake. Gigante surprises everyone when he switches sides and joins Nicole and Marche against his brother David and Jake. Things look good for the new threesome until Glen and Sting arrive and join the battle, determined to ...

13.title: A New World
13.plot: Odin surprises everyone when he refuses to battle Sho and turns his Bey to battle Ryan instead. Ryan defeats Odin and then challenges Sho to a final battle to see who will be the one to open the portal and go forth into the new world. Meanwhile Covey, Marche, Nicole and Gigante defeat David, Jake, Glen and Sting and Jin and Leon defeat Mathew and Lucy. In the final battle between Ryan and Sho, Sho is in big trouble but uses the power of all the feelings of every opponent and friend he has encountered on his journey and he and Pegasus defeat Ryan and Kerbecs. -1.title: Race: The Beywheelz Grand Prix
-1.plot: Sho and Jin travel to Das Vegas, where they hope to find strong bladers who will join them in their quest to defeat the Dominators. They watch a match that takes place in a huge arena, but Jin thinks the competitors, Nicole and Marche, are really just entertainers, not true bladers. Nicole is incensed by this and challenges Team Estrella to a battle to prove they are for real. Sho and Jin accept and they win, but Jin is so impressed by their skills that he asks them if they will help them defeat the Dominators, an offer that Nicole and Marche accept.

imdb.plot outline: BeyWheelz is set in the futuristic city of Destection where our hero, Sho, is champion of the BeyWheelz World Tournament! This peaceful city is home to exciting and challenging battles between friends and allies until suddenly the city is attacked by an evil BeyWheelz army called the Dominators who want control over all of the BeyWheelz in the world. With the future and freedom of BeyWheelz at stake, Sho and his friends take on the Dominators' strongest fighters in an epic battle of good vs. evil.
